### Get Order by ID with Authentication
# @name GetOrderRequest
## TEST-EXPECT-STATUS: [200]
## TEST-HAS-BODY
GET {{ApiBaseUrl}}/orders/{{CreateOrderRequest.response.body.$.id}}
Accept: application/json
X-Api-Key: {{ApiKey}}

